{"tid":1100852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過去3年117正規警員被捕 休班警佔逾7成","createTime":"2019-04-10T16:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T00:20:07.000Z","uid":5195,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0167f33e9a068e4fae062a7fb7e224cb90e838c2","tid":1100852,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1477053/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1477053%2F&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=6d3c7c3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1477053%2F&h=44e58823\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1477053/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方資料顯示，由2016年至2018年，被警方拘捕的正規警務人員分別有34、18及38人，當中分別有21、15及30人涉嫌干犯警隊定義為罪行性質屬較嚴重的刑事案件，而相關案件一般由刑事調查單位處理。<br />\n<br />\n據警隊了解，在過去3年，每年分別有9、11及7名正規警務人員被廉政公署及海關等其他執法部門拘捕。在上述的所有被捕警務人員中，過去3年每年分別有33、23及31名警務人員在休班期間涉案被捕，佔過去3年總數約74%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警隊於去年使用隨身攝錄機共拍攝275段影片，比前年的384段下跌。而截至今年2月底，有48段影片被警方保留超過558日，當中45段為處理公眾活動期間所錄影的片段。"},{"pid":"18ce15e04bb48b1192ad3650e2a0e2adaa7be448","tid":1100852,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"今年呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇下有幾多單個別事件 周高層震怒左幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe6816ef767236032c2f1c56ee941fa07e83fa5","tid":1100852,"uid":44117,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"平均3,4 日一隻警犬<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8805f790330a33a0b359b4a9de2bed3aefc53e0f","tid":1100852,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T16:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWdwOGV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%